title: Dozens of Indians missing in Iraq since 2014 found dead
text:
Dozens of Indians missing in Iraq since 2014 found dead 9:03pm IST - 01:03 
India has confirmed that the bodies of 39 Indian construction workers thought to have been kidnapped by Islamic State militias in 2014 have been found in a mass grave in Mosul.
